kup?title=Cholera+country+profile&amp;publication_year=2006&amp;" target="pmc_ext" ref="reftype=other&amp;article-id=2669128&amp;issue-id=177493&amp;journal-id=532&amp;FROM=Article%7CCitationRef&amp;TO=Content%20Provider%7CLink%7CGoogle%20Scholar">Google Scholar</a>]</span></span></div><div class="ref-cit-blk half_rhythm" id="pntd.0000335-Peiris1">12. <span class="element-citation">Peiris J, Yuen K, Osterhaus A, St&#x000f6;hr K. The severe acute respiratory syndrome. <span><span class="ref-journal">N Engl J Med. </span>2003;<span class="ref-vol">349</span>:2431\xe2\x80\x932441.</span> [<a href="/pubmed/14681510" target="pmc_ext" ref="reftype=pubmed&amp;article-id=2669128&amp;issue-id=177493&amp;journal-id=532&amp;FROM=Article%7CCitationRef&amp;TO=Entrez%7CPubMed%7CRecord">PubMed</a>] <span class="nowrap">[<a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?journal=N+Engl+J+Med&amp;title=The+severe+acute+respiratory+syndrome.&amp;author=J+Peiris&amp;author=K+Yuen&amp;author=A+Osterhaus&amp;author=K+St&#x000f6;hr&amp;volume=349&amp;publication_year=2003&amp;pages=2431-2441&amp;pmid=14681510&amp;" target="pmc_ext" ref="reftype=other&amp;article-id=2669128&amp;issue-id=177493&amp;journal-id=532&amp;FROM=Article%7CCitationRef&amp;TO=Content%20Provider%7CLink%7CGoogle%20Scholar">Google Scholar</a>]</span></span></div><div class="ref-cit-blk half_rhythm" id="pntd.0000335-Ho1">13. <span class="element-citation">Ho J, Ooi G, Mok T, Chan J, Hung I, et al.  High-dose pulse versus nonpulse corticosteroid regimens in severe acute respiratory syndrome. <span><span class="ref-journal">Am J Respir Crit Care Med. </span>2003;<span class="ref-vol">168</span>:1449\xe2\x80\x931456.</span> [<a href="/pubmed/12947028" target="pmc_ext" ref="reftype=pubmed&amp;article-id=2669128&amp;issue-id=177493&amp;journal-id=532&amp;FROM=Article%7CCitationRef&amp;TO=Entrez%7CPubMed%7CRecord">PubMed</a>] <span class="nowrap">[<a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?journal=Am+J+Respir+Crit+Ca